Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs24\c&H322722&\fad(50,0)\pos(480,649)}昨天看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs24\c&H322722&\fad(50,0)\pos(280,648.6)}之前的森川？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs24\c&H322722&\fad(50,0)\pos(406.4,648.6)}之后的森川
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs24\c&H322722&\fad(50,0)\pos(320,650)}为什么不告诉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs25\c&H322722&\fad(50,0)\pos(350.4,578)}因为很期待你的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs20\c&H322722&\frz350.7\pos(568.4,385)\1a&H3C&}森川是不是发生了什么事
